      • WriteAccessHandlerFilteringRepository

        public WriteAccessHandlerFilteringRepository(org.eclipse.emf.cdo.spi.server.InternalRepository delegate,
                                             boolean notifyWriteAccesshandlers)
        Creates a delegating repository instance. This repository instance could be configured to ignore notifying all registered write access handlers to the delegating repository.
        Parameters:
        delegate - the delegate repository.
        notifyWriteAccesshandlers - false if the WriteAccessHandler should not be notified about changes, otherwise false.
